<p> RAD focuses on Integrated Farming System (IFS) for enhancing productivity and minimizing risks associated with climatic variabilityâ€™s. Under this system, crops/cropping system is integrated with activities like horticulture, livestock, fishery, agro-forestry, apiculture etc. to enable farmers not only in maximizing farm returns for sustaining livelihood, but also to mitigate the impacts of drought, flood or other extreme weather events with the income opportunity from allied activities during crop damage.
<br>
<a href="https://nmsa.dac.gov.in/frmComponents.aspx"><h4>Apply</h4></a>

</p>
</div>

